      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in unparalleled condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin environment, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom delivery. Mechanically definitive and aesthetically beyond reproach, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly superlative driving machine.",
